{"tid":2247300,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"周國賢 x 黃偉文 香港預言三步曲 【我們•今生•在】","createTime":"2020-10-17T17:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T09:37:51.000Z","uid":35021,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4065ee794307a2f16a9692cb0bfbfd8c390399e5","tid":2247300,"uid":35021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:24:23.000Z","msg":"周國賢同小克嘅 New Age 三步曲， 相信好多人都認識，甚至早過 Christopher Nolan 電影 【Interstellar】面世。去到2020年，同Wyman合作，未必有咁多人留意嘅另外三步曲，當日預視香港我城衰落，香港人離家出走，對前人留下美好被糟蹋嘅無力，已經一一成為現在進行式。<br />\n<br />\n《我們都不是無辜的》<br />\n表面講分居、離婚， 內裡講嘅喺香港同中国嘅關係。口裏說愛，實際在拉鋸拔海<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQkioKadAk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQkioKadAk8&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=0f7bf26f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQkioKadAk8</a><br />\n<br />\n《今生不回家》<br />\n開始寫得明顯少少，講傘革之後考慮移民嘅心態，經過反送中抗爭同国安法，已成新一波移民潮。 曾以為有家就是安穩，當天氣改變世道人心......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjqzQq28QUAc&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=cfa985ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jqzQq28QUAc</a><br />\n<br />\n《在天之靈》<br />\n最終章畫公仔畫出腸。昔日守護、建設香港嘅英靈， 望住今日崛起嘅禽獸......<br />\n<br />\n自上幼稚園 推銷那醜陋 <br />\n孩子不聽 要批鬥<br />\n人間的新審美 你明了沒有<br />\n路過意外 亂拍一會 才去救 餵飽手機渴求<br />\n鍵盤愛刻薄 誰要理由 隨手打兩篇毒咒<br />\n<br />\n聽講所有撕裂 搞show可以補救 <br />\n豪宅必須供應 農田還剩五六畝<br />\n飯要開 無謂說真話 <br />\n回家post個 「嬲嬲」足夠 <br />\n我是時候自戴手扣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/coqhPjwFivQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcoqhPjwFivQ&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=646b60c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/coqhPjwFivQ</a><br />\n<br />\n外傳 - 《消化不良》林寶 填詞<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文填詞人聯盟成員，傘革後直接宣泄嘅歌曲，689三隻字都放埋MV，仲直接過方皓玟個《虛偽》MV。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b4bttiv8wLY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb4bttiv8wLY&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=4e981f60\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b4bttiv8wLY</a>"},{"pid":"c0abf9a5a80cf6eeeb86ac97ff94899b48683e1f","tid":2247300,"uid":226573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ed6befc0446b5825540aadd23da327cd8615e608","tid":2247300,"uid":49367,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"最愛周爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1a77c2050e58665419cc663e3a2e2937208cac","tid":2247300,"uid":366245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:30:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3bfcc5b3479bc25271d0a19cbba092e40829903","tid":2247300,"uid":366245,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc44f366a163d227f6add61e4d1c739e59abe2a8","tid":2247300,"uid":379488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"真係唔明點解佢紅唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d75d68ae27bf33baefa82d94def3f72775a9278","tid":2247300,"uid":80503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"以前聽唔明覺得唔好聽<br />\n依家聽返就覺得佢行得太前<br />\n建議首推銷員之死"},{"pid":"33d8122ecb2715dfe8dcc68b4d34ec482e783588","tid":2247300,"uid":15081,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2d75d68ae27bf33baefa82d94def3f72775a9278","tid":2247300,"uid":80503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"以前聽唔明覺得唔好聽<br />\n依家聽返就覺得佢行得太前<br />\n建議首推銷員之死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:52:17.000Z","msg":"推銷員之死真係聽到灰，歌詞太到肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ee1b9a8a5553b440b86df2244d894f907a2423","tid":2247300,"uid":60047,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2d75d68ae27bf33baefa82d94def3f72775a9278","tid":2247300,"uid":80503,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score"